high_descs: Move forward, then turn right and go to the blue chair.
Pick up the leftmost pillow on the blue chair.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to face the sofa.
Put the pillow on the sofa, to the right of the newspaper.
Turn left, and go back to the blue chair.
Pick up the pillow on the blue chair.
Turn left, move forward, turn left, then turn left again to face the sofa.
Put the pillow on the sofa, to the left of the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two pillows on the sofa.

high_descs: take a few steps forward and turn to the right and go to the blue chair
pick up the left pillow on the chair
turn to the right twice and take a few steps forward and turn to the left facing the sofa
put the pillow on the sofa right of the newspaper
step forward to the sofa and turn to the left and go to the blue chair
pick up the pillow on the chair
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the left facing the sofa
put the pillow on the sofa left of the newspaper
anns.task_desc: Place two pillows on a sofa

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the blue chair with two pillows on its seat.
Pick up the leftmost pillow off of the seat of the chair.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the couch.
Put the pillow vertically on the couch to the right of the newspaper.
Turn left and walk over to the blue chair.
Pick up the pillow off of the seat of the blue chair.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk over to the couch.
Put the pillow vertically on the couch to the left of the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Move two pillows to the couch.
